{"type":"message","id":"7958fa58","parentId":"dffaa4be","timestamp":"2026-04-16T09:06:18.345Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"What does DORA measures?"}],"timestamp":1776330378341}}
{"type":"message","id":"729db05a","parentId":"7958fa58","timestamp":"2026-04-16T09:06:21.626Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"DORA measures **software delivery performance**.\n\nThe four classic DORA metrics are:\n\n1. **Deployment Frequency**  \n   How often you deploy to production.\n\n2. **Lead Time for Changes**  \n   How long it takes for a code change to go from commit to production.\n\n3. **Change Failure Rate**  \n   The percentage of deployments that cause a failure in production.\n\n4. **Time to Restore Service**  \n   How long it takes to recover from a production incident or outage.\n\nThese metrics are used to assess how effectively and reliably a team delivers software.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0f48c10ae20cd87b0169e0a68b69f88191bf4ef8a23150cb4e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":3990,"output":119,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":4109,"cost":{"input":0.009975000000000001,"output":0.0017850000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.011760000000000001}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776330378346,"responseId":"resp_0f48c10ae20cd87b0169e0a68abdf88191a5f23188673b3008"}}
